The profession of a tiler is one of the most popular in the construction industry, and specialists in thfield can easily find a job in construction companies and enterprises.

Facing worker-tiler
finishes building facades with ceramic and concrete slabs;
performs laying of stone and concrete steps of external stairs;
installs bollards of fences and parapets made of hewn stone;
performs facing of embankments and bridge spans;
performs work on the installation of tiled floors and facing the internal surfaces of the walls of baths, laundries, sanitary units, bathrooms;
sorts ceramic tiles by type, size, color;
prepares solutions, cleans surfaces before laying ceramic tiles;
repair a tiled surface.
